text = "Player:
WASD - Move
Shift - Sprint
Space - Jump
Mouse - Look
Esc - Unlock Cursor
M/Tab - Open world map

World map:
Drag - Pan
Wheel - Zoom
V - Toggle shader
C - Toggle contours
B - Toggle major contours
G - Toggle shading ramp
I - Toggle invert"
